1. top- task manager esc
2. pidof <process> - process id of
3. pkill <process> - process kill (all instances)
4. kill <pid> - killing particular instance of that process
5. gzip <filename> - compress a single file
6. gunzip <filename> - extracting
7. tar - (tape archive) single archive out of multiple files 
      [ tar -c for create || tar -cf to creat and write into file || <file>.tar f1 f2 d3... ]
      [ tar -tvf to view all files in the zip || tar -xf   to extract the files ]
8. * (wildcard) - to tar all one type of files
